  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the crushed tomatoes, mustard seeds, dried oregano, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the pasta to the pot, stirring to coat with the tomato sauce.",
    "Add 4 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15-20 minutes, or until the pasta is al dente.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh basil and serve hot."
